      ARTHUR ELLIOTT
 (Police sergeant, GIS
). I saw the prisoner Walk into the room—he kicked Sergeant Leather on the knee, who came down upon his knees, and I knocked the prisoner down—ho dropped a packet from his hand—I held him while Leather took the packets from his pocket.
